{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Welcome
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
	<section class="container my-5 mx-auto fs-4">
		<div class="row text-btn fw-light align-items-center mx-1">
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 bg-div-home p-3 my-2">
				<p>Are you prepared for the unexpected ?
				Tired of throwing away expired food and wasting money ?
				Looking for a good food stock tracking tool ?
				Good news, you've found it !</p>
				<img src="{{ asset('build/icon/myInventory.png') }}" class="div-home-logo" alt="my inventory logo">
			</div>
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 d-none d-md-block">
				<img src="{{ asset ('build/images/canned1.jpg') }}" alt="canned_image" class="div-home-image"></div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="row text-btn fw-light align-items-center mx-1">
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 d-none d-md-block"><img src="{{ asset ('build/images/canned2.jpg') }}" alt="canned_image" class="div-home-image"></div>
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 bg-div-home p-3 my-2">
				<p>myIn<span class="v-style">v</span>entory allows you to easily keep track
				of your non-perishable food reserve and
				make sure that you have enough supplies
				for any emergency and alerts you when a
				product is approaching its expiration date.
				Not only will this save you money, but it
				also helps reduce food waste and is
				better for the environment.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="row text-btn fw-light align-items-center mx-1">
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 bg-div-home p-3 my-2">
				<p>Keeping track of your food stock also
				ensures that you eat healthy by preventing
				you from reaching for that old bag of chips
				hiding in the back of your pantry.
				Register and let's make sure that you'll be
				reminded when it's time to rotate your stock,
				ensuring that your emergency food supply
				is always fresh and ready to go.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 d-none d-md-block"><img src="{{ asset ('build/images/canned3.jpg') }}" alt="canned_image" class="div-home-image"></div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="row text-btn fw-light align-items-center mx-1">
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 d-none d-md-block"><img src="{{ asset ('build/images/canned4.jpg') }}" alt="canned_image" class="div-home-image"></div>
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 bg-div-home p-3 my-2 v-image">
				<p>Don't let your food become a science
				experiment, don't be caught off guard,
				join us now and take control of your
				food supply. Sign up now and
				kiss those moldy leftovers goodbye !</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
{% endblock %}
